 the deal was canceled last minute for publicly undisclosed reasons in may  the primerica executive team led by coceos john addison and rick williams approached private equity firm jc flowers  co yet again as well as blackstone group lp and tpg inc  in a new attempt to have the company bought a plan which citigroup did not endorse initial public offering on november   citi announced that it intended to spin off primerica through an initial public offering the primerica executive and legal team filed an s with the us securities and exchange commission sec having officially publicly announced the intention of becoming a public company citi would claim all profit from the primary offering as well as continue to receive income from a significant portion of existing primerica business with citi holdings ceo michael corbit claiming the move to be the best separation alternative for this franchise primerica filed a final amended s and preliminary prospectus with the sec on march   indicating that it will offer  million shares to the public through the ipo with underwriters having the option to purchase an additional  million shares the first trading occurred on april   initially the expected share price was in the  –  range having ended up being priced  a share on march   resulting in citi raising  percent or  million more than  million projected through the ipo by selling  million more shares than the anticipated  million the first day of trading saw the stock surge  percent to end up closing at  a share in a separate offering private equity firm warburg pincus has bought  million shares resulting in a  percent stake in primerica and up to  percent if warburg decides to exercise warrants to purchase an additional  million shares from citi following the ipo citis stake was between  percent and  percent and expected to divest its interest in primerica as soon as possible to fulfill its original goal of raising cash by shedding assets to improve financial performance on december   citigroup sold its remaining equity stake in primerica approximately  million shares of primericas common stock completing the separation from citi awards primerica life insurance company and its new york subsidiary national benefit life have received several awards from a m best standard  poors and the insurance marketplace standards association imsa for their financial strength high standards and quality business primerica has also received awards for customer service see also brokerage firm financial institution references  a b seward christopher january   primerica names glenn williams as ceo atlanta journal constitution retrieved february     a b c d e company overview  a b primerica reports fourth quarter  results business wire february   retrieved march     pri – research and analysis for primerica inc msn money retrieved march     a b primerica ipo citigroup unwinds its farflung empire bloggingstocks  retrieved    peter schneider et al  comment of primerica financial services inc on the revised notice of proposed rulemaking on the business opportunity rule r pdf federal trade commission archived from the original pdf on  retrieved    a b primerica reports fourth quarter  results businesswire february   retrieved march     primerica financial services inc may   comment of primerica financial services inc on the revised notice of proposed rulemaking on the business opportunity rule r pdf federal trade commission protecting americas consumers pp – retrieved january   primerica suggests three modifications to the rpbor to better assure that the regulatory language actually achieves the clear intent of the revised notice that the rule exclude multilevel marketing opportunities like those offered by primerica and by many members of the direct selling association   duluth city georgia us census bureau retrieved on july    contact us primerica retrieved on march   corporate address primerica inc  primerica parkway duluth ga  united states  a b primericas hist