nt to end up closing at  a share in a separate offering private equity firm warburg pincus has bought  million shares resulting in a  percent stake in primerica and up to  percent if warburg decides to exercise warrants to purchase an additional  million shares from citi following the ipo citis stake was between  percent and  percent and expected to divest its interest in primerica as soon as possible to fulfill its original goal of raising cash by shedding assets to improve financial performance on december   citigroup sold its remaining equity stake in primerica approximately  million shares of primericas common stock completing the separation from citi awards primerica life insurance company and its new york subsidiary national benefit life have received several awards from a m best standard  poors and the insurance marketplace standards association imsa for their financial strength high standards and quality business primerica has also received awards for customer service see also brokerage firm financial institution references  a b seward christopher january   primerica names glenn williams as ceo atlanta journal constitution retrieved february     a b c d e company overview  a b primerica reports fourth quarter  results business wire february   retrieved march     pri – research and analysis for primerica inc msn money retrieved march     a b primerica ipo citigroup unwinds its farflung empire bloggingstocks  retrieved    peter schneider et al  comment of primerica financial services inc on the revised notice of proposed rulemaking on the business opportunity rule r pdf federal trade commission archived from the original pdf on  retrieved    a b primerica reports fourth quarter  results businesswire february   retrieved march     primerica financial services inc may   comment of primerica financial services inc on the revised notice of proposed rulemaking on the business opportunity rule r pdf federal trade commission protecting americas consumers pp – retriev